# wasabaaeee Live Follower Count Tracker Configuration Template
# Copy this file to '.env' in the same folder to enable live integrations.

# ==============================================================================
# Method A: Instagram Web Session Cookie (Highly Recommended, Free)
# ==============================================================================
# To scrape Sobi's follower count directly from Instagram without getting a 401 error:
# 1. Open your browser and log into instagram.com
# 2. Open DevTools (F12 or Cmd+Opt+I)
# 3. Go to the "Application" tab (Chrome) or "Storage" tab (Safari/Firefox)
# 4. Under Cookies -> https://www.instagram.com, find the cookie named 'sessionid'
# 5. Copy its value and paste it below:
# INSTAGRAM_SESSION_ID=your_sessionid_cookie_value_here

# ==============================================================================
# Method B: RapidAPI Subscription (Paid / Freemium Scraper)
# ==============================================================================
# If you prefer to route scraping requests through a paid proxy service on RapidAPI:
# 1. Sign up on rapidapi.com and subscribe to an Instagram scraper API
# 2. Enter your API Key and host name below:
# RAPIDAPI_KEY=your_rapidapi_key_here
# RAPIDAPI_HOST=instagram-scraper-api2.p.rapidapi.com
